[b]Compatibility[/b]
Compatible with the latest version of Subnautica. Built for BepInEx and Nautilus.


[b]Installation[/b]
[list]
[*] Install BepInEx and Nautilus
[*] Place the mod files in your BepInEx plugins folder
[*] Launch the game
[/list]


[b]Uninstallation[/b]
Remove the mod files from the BepInEx plugins folder.


[b]Notes[/b]
Changing settings only apply to newly spawned Reaper Leviathans. For existing Reapers, exit and re-load your save to see changes.